Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各位早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在大地震屆滿6週年的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各地正舉行各種悼念祭來…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 連桿上有裂紋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒拿去店裡修嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要修理引擎的話 已經沒那麼多社團經費了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台是自己組裝的機器 所以想自己修修看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}接下來是關於政治與經濟的報道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GGP治安維持部隊的最高負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(30,280)}GGP治安維持部隊\N新司令官 今日上任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}羅曼洛夫·卡連巴古大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子上收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有社團活動 我為了不忘記…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的比賽後 感覺好像發現了什麼靈感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Rideback的騎術又或者是自我真實能力展現的方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 琳 妳還記得今天是什麼日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是站前商場舉行大甩賣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說好跟妳一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的 搭檔 別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就先去逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是好高興呢 琳找到了能讓自己如此專注的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那不是Rideback嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}…計劃投入警察部隊的特殊車輛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}通稱的「白Ride」 首次對媒體公開發表了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\fs22}「白Ride」:為了理解我們之後也會翻為「警用Rideback」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(40,290)}警察特殊車輛「白Ride」對媒體發表
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:46.73,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:46.73,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:48.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:48.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:06.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:06.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:30.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:30.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:33.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:33.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:42.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:42.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:48.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:48.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
